Paper Code: ETTE-356 L T/P C
Paper: Mould Design-I Lab 0 2 1


List of Experiments:


1. Study of basic elements of two plate mould design

2. Study and design of different types of gates used in injection moulding.

3. Design and study of Different types of runners.

4. Study the working principle of ejector plate assembly

5. Study the working principle of different types of ejector pins.

6. Design of integer core/cavity cooling circuit.

7. Design of insert core/cavity cooling circuit.

8. Study of heat pipe/heat rod method for conducting heat from core/cavity of injection mould.

9. Study and design the layout of gate and runner balancing.

10. Study of injection moulding machine.

11. Study the defects and remedies of injection moulded parts.


NOTE: - At least 8 Experiments out of the list must be done in the semester.